/p><p>为了庆祝入驻，Hagar 和 Anthony 将于周日（11 月 24 日）在忠诚体育场举行的拉斯维加斯突袭者队对阵丹佛野马队的比赛中场表演中进行表演。新闻稿称，演出将向美国军事人员致敬，“为他们的勇敢和服务提供特别的惊喜”。</p><p> 11 月 9 日周末，Hagar 和 Guy Fieri 的联合龙舌兰酒公司 Santo Tequila 在德克萨斯州遭遇劫持，窃贼偷走了两辆卡车，其中载有约 100 万美元（788,892.40 英镑）的商品。</p><p>据<a href="https://www.foxnews.com/entertainment/guy-fieri-sammy-hagars-trucks-carrying-1-million-tequila-hijacked-after-crossing-u-s-border" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>福克斯新闻报道</em></a>，Hagar 的一名代表透露，这些卡车在越过边境进入美国后在拉雷多被盗。共有 4,040 箱龙舌兰酒（24,240 瓶）被盗。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/DCcCw17vrcE/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="https://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"><g stroke="none" stroke-width="1" fill="none" fill-rule="evenodd"><g transform="translate(-511.000000, -20.000000)" fill="#000000"><g><path d="M556.869,30.41 C554.814,30.41 553.148,32.076 553.148,34.131 C553.148,36.186 554.814,37.852 556.869,37.852 C558.924,37.852 560.59,36.186 560.59,34.131 C560.59,32.