//www.nme.com/series/baby-reindeer">《小驯鹿》的</a>创作者理查德·加德 (Richard Gadd) <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/tv/baby-reindeer-creator-richard-gadd-the-pogues-inspired-him-3755983">公开了肖恩·麦高恩 (Shane MacGowan) 和波格斯乐队 (The Pogues) 如何影响他的作品</a>。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-pogues-announce-2025-uk-and-ireland-tour-celebrating-40-years-of-rum-sodomy-the-lash-3813788">The Pogues 宣布 2025 年英国和爱尔兰巡演庆祝“Rum Sodomy &amp; The Lash”40 周年的</a>帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
